##Wuhan Nursing Home Asks for help

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

@ wuhan.com

On February 21, the Wuhan Bureau of Civil Affairs responded to the Internet Query:

1 NUCLEIC ACID test and CT scan were carried out in Wuhan Social Welfare Institute, 12 people were diagnosed and one person died. Confirmed, suspected cases were immediately transferred to the relevant medical institutions for treatment, there is no online said "11 old people died of respiratory failure" situation.

2 detailed introduction Qiao Estuary Thou Farmland Financial Health Care Center death of the elderly sick the whole process.

3. Prioritize. Next, NUCLEIC ACID testing will be carried out on all staff in Wuhan old-age Care Institutions. FULL NUCLEIC ACID testing is completed by 22 February for institutions with confirmed and suspected cases, and by 28 February for other institutions.

I. General Information

(I) Wuhan Social Welfare home

Wuhan Social Welfare Hospital, designed bed 814 beds, with Wuhan Jimin Hospital for the elderly, with an outpatient department, a rehabilitation ward and a comprehensive ward. The hospital is located in the center of the outbreak (south China Seafood Market) opposite, prevention and control difficulties, high infection rate. At the time of the outbreak, there were a total of 656 people in the hospital, including 458 clients (80 self-care elderly, 56 referrals, 322 referrals) , 190 employees, 21 property staff, 8 escorts. As of February 19, the hospital has confirmed 12 cases, including 11 elderly (including one death) , 1 employee; 19 suspected cases, including 7 elderly, 12 employees, all confirmed and suspected personnel have been sent to quarantine points, shelter hospitals and designated hospitals for classified treatment.

The hospital from January 21 began to implement closed management, January 24 in the Han hospital staff stop leave, immediately return to work, eat and live in hospital, all personnel except medical and living supplies prohibited access. In the early stage of the epidemic, the hospital carried out infection prevention and control according to the "two districts and three channels" measures according to the expert opinions assigned by the Municipal Commission of Health and hygiene. In view of the objective difficulties such as the tense state of medical resources and the mobility inconvenience of the elderly in the hospital in the early stage of the epidemic in Wuhan, in order to avoid the risk of infection, the hospital has set up a temporary observation area for fever patients in the hospital. The patients with suspected symptoms of new pneumonia, such as fever and cough, will be isolated for observation.

After the relative relaxation of medical resources, in order to more accurately implement the classified management of the elderly in the hospital, after many contacts with the district CDC, the hospital received 40 samples on February 11, February 14,300 samples of nucleic acid test tubes, suspected personnel in the hospital for sampling and inspection. Since February 16th, additional CT scans have been added. For the screening of confirmed, suspected cases immediately transferred to the relevant medical institutions, there is no online report that 11 elderly people died of repeated fever, respiratory failure problems.

At present, all the cases in the hospital, except one old man died on the way to hospital, 9 cases were transferred to the city Youfu Hospital, 9 cases were transferred to Caidian square cabin, 7 cases were transferred to Hubei Integrated Hospital of traditional Chinese and Western medicine Two people to the street designated hotel isolation treatment.

Because the epidemic period occurred during the Spring Festival, some of the nursing staff returned to their hometown. During the epidemic period, all the nursing staff and medical staff in the hospital had to participate in the nursing service for the elderly. Therefore, some of the medical staff were infected. The nurse of the hospital, Lu Mou, was found to have pneumonia when she was examined, the first nucleic acid test is negative, at the Jiashiting hotel isolation observation.

(2) Qiao Estuary Thou Farmland Financial Rehabilitation Center situation

After verification, the online report reflected the elderly Hu mou-fang (female, 85 years old, is a semi-self-care elderly, 30 years of high blood pressure history) , on August 15,2018, with her husband in the Qiao estuary integration of Gutian elderly apartment in room 708. At 22:05 p.m. on February 14,2020, the hospital found that Hu had a fever of 38.5 degrees during a body temperature test, but he said that he had no other complaints. The hospital treated him with antipyretic suppository and oral medication, and the old man told his daughter by telephone, suggested out for an examination, but his daughter said first in the hospital observation. The old man's temperature dropped to 36.8 degrees after two hours of medication. His temperature was normal that night. Because the old man had fever and lived in the same room as her husband Xiao, the hospital asked for isolation, but the old man refused to be separated, the hospital can only arrange the old man and his wife to live together temporarily.

February 15,16 normal body temperature, occasionally cough phenomenon, poor appetite. February 16, the paramedic Liu see spirit is not good, the old man self-described loss of appetite, breathing difficulties, immediately inform the doctor. After checking the body temperature, blood pressure, heartbeat, breath found that its heart rate accelerated, mouth cyanosis, the initial assessment of inflammation in the lungs. The hospital immediately gave him oxygen therapy, and repeatedly contacted his family members to go out for examination and treatment, informing them that his life was in danger at any time. However, his family members refused to go to the hospital all along on the grounds that they were forbidden to travel in the urban area, and the building was unable to leave because of fever, only antiviral drug, herbal decoction and oxygen inhalation can be used for conservative treatment in the medical institutions set up in the hospital.

From February 17 to 18, the old man's condition was stable, mental improvement, and also with his family video call, but February 19, the old man's condition deteriorated, died of respiratory failure at 6:15 a.m. unfortunately. After the old man died, the hospital first time to inform the family, the family can not go out on the grounds of community closure, not to the nursing home to deal with the funeral. Through Qiao Estuary Bureau of Civil Affairs repeatedly coordination, February 19 at 4:30 pm, his son Xiao agreed to sign a trust agreement, full power to entrust the nursing home for the elderly funeral.

Hu mou-fen has been responsible for the care worker Liu mou, Liu myself at present physical symptoms normal, no fever and so on. The nurse, surnamed Tang, reported to have been working in a nursing home since the Lunar New Year and had not returned to Hanchuan and had no contact with the man. Another nurse, surnamed Zhang, also had no contact with the man and was transferred to a shelter hospital on Feb. 11 because of fever and CT findings. Because the old man did not do CT and nucleic acid testing, and the care of the old man is normal, the old man can not be classified as a suspected case.

2. Disposal of relevant matters

On February 19 and 20, the person in charge of the Wuhan Social Welfare home made several face-to-face communications to the isolation point, but the person concerned was emotional and said the hotel had no medical protection, requesting immediate transfer to shelter. Because according to the regulations, did not pass the nucleic acid test positive, temporarily can not transfer to the shelter hospital. At present, arrangements have been made for their nucleic acid test again, while trying to meet the requirements of the parties, for understanding and support.

Qiao Estuary Bureau of Civil Affairs, Rongji Thou farmland elderly apartment is also in charge of the parties to explain communication.

In the future, Wuhan authorities will take the following measures:

First, the strict implementation of territorial responsibility. All the city's elderly institutions in accordance with the territorial principle, a leak, a person does not fall into the community investigation and control management, strict implementation of the Wuhan Municipal Party Committee "five hundred percent" work requirements.

Second, all personnel to carry out nucleic acid testing. Prioritize and complete all nucleic acid testing by February 22 for institutions with confirmed and suspected cases, and by February 28 for other institutions.

Third, the establishment of a green channel for medical treatment. For those who test positive for nucleic acid in old-age institutions, they will be admitted unconditionally by the medical treatment team of Wuhan Command and designated hospitals in all districts. Suspected cases will be sent to isolation points for observation at the first time to avoid reporting at the community, street and district levels.

Fourth, early isolation should be carried out resolutely. In accordance with the standards for prevention and control of centralized isolation points at the district level, the district health and disease control departments shall, in accordance with the standards, provide professional medical and nursing personnel, and bring them into the statistical scope and standardized management of centralized isolation points under their jurisdiction.

Fifth, strengthen the nursing force of the old-age care institutions. The financial, social and civil affairs departments of Wuhan and the district shall adopt measures such as granting temporary work subsidies, urgent recruitment and training, and strengthening the deployment of nursing staff to strengthen the nursing force of old-age institutions and stabilize the nursing staff.

Wuhan Bureau of Civil Affairs
February 20,2020
